{
  "id": "adv_event_2303_01_03",
  "title": "わちゃわちゃ\n合宿\n買い出し隊",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんっとーーに申し訳ありません！\n私のために、合宿まで開催してもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I'm really sorry!\nThank you all for organizing this training camp for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.681790467000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8857588965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、今日中に新ユニットを決めないといけないって\n聞いた時は、さすがにびっくりしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ when I heard we had to decide on a new unit today‚\nI was really surprised‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8857588965,
      "endTime": 15.4331963737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.6190922299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "困った時は合宿！　合宿すればなんとかなる！\n星見プロの伝統ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When in trouble‚ we camp! Camping will solve everything!\nIt's a tradition at Hoshimi Pro.!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6190922299,
      "endTime": 21.5737415472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.7416789252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "そういう精神論みたいなの、こころはどうかと\n思いますけど～。でも、ちょっと楽しそうですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is not sure about that kind of spiritualism‚\nbut… it sounds a bit fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7416789252,
      "endTime": 29.703379650800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9100464701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、買い出しにまで付き合ってくれて\nありがとうございます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for coming with me\neven to the shopping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9100464701,
      "endTime": 35.3219283938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤さんと白石さんも、別の所で準備を進めてくれて\n……星見プロのアイドルは天使……いや、女神！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to Hyodo-san and Shiraishi-san preparing elsewhere‚\n…Hoshimi Pro.'s idols are angels… no‚ goddesses!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.508323423,
      "endTime": 45.1929034868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.46
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4595705349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……えへへ。そうなのかも、しれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ehehe. Maybe that's true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4595705349,
      "endTime": 49.6679832298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0004823565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "合宿！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Camp!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3676190454,
      "endTime": 53.682267304199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8544949453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。こういう時は合宿に限りますわ\n一晩あれば時間は十分！　やりますわよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. In times like this‚ nothing beats a camp.\nOne night should be enough time! Let's do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8544949453,
      "endTime": 61.4999879339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6372894526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……うん。確かに、それが一番かも\n合宿の場所は……時間もないし私達の寮にするとして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. That might be the best idea.\nAs for the camp location… since we're out of time‚ let's use our dorm as the campsite.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6372894526,
      "endTime": 72.7513487101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9372894526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "合宿に必要な物は、みんなで手分けして用意しないと\n買い出し班と、寮で合宿の準備をする班に分かれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to divide the necessary items for the camp and prepare together…\nWe should divide into shopping team and camp preparation team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9372894526,
      "endTime": 82.92595198160001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1372894526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、こころは買い出し班を希望です\nみんなが大好きなお菓子を大量に買っておきます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'd like to be on the shopping team.\nI'll buy lots of everyone's favorite snacks~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1372894526,
      "endTime": 90.01989719870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.213230284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！　それじゃ私も買い出し班希望ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! Then I want to be on the shopping team too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.213230284,
      "endTime": 94.31536384420001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.5086971204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "私も……いや、じゃあ私は、準備の方にしよっかな\n資料集めとか、お泊りの用意とかいろいろやらないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll… well‚ then I'll handle the preparations.\nThere's a lot to do like gathering materials and preparing for the overnight stay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5086971204,
      "endTime": 105.9897178571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6086972118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、そっちは私達がやるから\n買い出し班の方に行ってきたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ since we'll take care of the materials‚\nwhy don't you join the shopping team?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.175363787,
      "endTime": 111.7845702727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.975363787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.975363787,
      "endTime": 112.958292528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.1420340141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "資料を……集めたり、整理するのは……\n星見プロで、一番得意。……多分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gathering and organizing materials is…\nSomething I'm best at in Hoshimi Pro… probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1420340141,
      "endTime": 120.2088483174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3705163877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、みんなをまとめようとして\n今日はずっと、頑張ってくれてたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you've been trying to lead\neveryone today‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3705163877,
      "endTime": 126.5189517897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.703849721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "前向きな意見を出して、みんなを引っ張ったり\n脱線を食い止めようとしたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Giving positive opinions‚ guiding everyone‚\ntrying to keep things on track…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.703849721,
      "endTime": 133.2320129633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4371830543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……あはは、ダメダメでしたけど\n瑠依ちゃんみたいに上手には出来ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haha‚ I didn't do very well‚ though.\nI'm not as good as Rui-chan at it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4371830543,
      "endTime": 140.56867976989997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7705163877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない。でも張り詰め過ぎても良くないよ\n買い出しで好きな物を買って、楽しんできなよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. But it's not good to push yourself.\nBuy what you like during shopping and enjoy it~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7705163877,
      "endTime": 150.12212638070002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.3371830543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
